description:
&quot;I wonder&hellip; if I&rsquo;ve become lecherous.&quot;

High school student Hiroki yearns for his best friend Yuuji's father, Seiji. He has tried many approaches, but has only managed brief exchanges. Yuuji told the depressed Hiroki &ldquo;I&rsquo;ve fallen in love with you&hellip;Why don&rsquo;t you forget about my father!&rdquo; However, Hiroki bravely began the process of captivating Seiji. Before long, the aimless lover is being loved, Hiroki&rsquo;s body being ravished&hellip;
In the shocking three part series, Idol Unit &ldquo;Boku-chan&rsquo;s*&rdquo; series. Drawn for this special release, a tank-full of even more love, debauchery, and worthwhile reading collected in this omnibus!!
